data.description: MOTIVATED TO SELL!  Come check out this home that features four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a fenced-in backyard! You'll have ample space to add a pool or let your furry friends play around. Great home for the first time home buyer or the growing family that needs more space.  The main bedroom boasts an attached bathroom, while the second bedroom comes with an ensuite bathroom that's wheelchair accessible, making it perfect for an in-law suite. Plus, the updated kitchen is equipped with newer cabinets, granite countertops, and a charming ''farmhouse'' sink. The house also has an updated hall bath and smart home features, including four security cameras, Sonos ceiling speakers, and lighting that can all be controlled through Alexa.
